    <item>
      <title>Brazil Oil Juniors 3R 与 Enauta 就 12 亿美元的交易达成一致</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-17/brazil-oil-junior-3r-agrees-to-buy-enauta-for-about-1-2-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西石油初级企业 3R Petroleum Oleo e Gas SA 同意以全股票交易收购 Enauta Participacoes SA，这是该国石油行业更广泛整合的最新举措，该公司股价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-17/brazil-oil-junior-3r-agrees-to-buy-enauta-for-about-1-2-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 13:53:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>现货白银突破每盎司 30 美元，创 2013 年以来新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-17/silver-tops-30-an-ounce-to-reach-highest-in-more-than-a-decade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[现货白银价格突破每盎司 30 美元，达到十多年来的最高水平，在金融和工业需求强劲的推动下，其涨势比黄金的涨势更为强劲、速度更快。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-17/silver-tops-30-an-ounce-to-reach-highest-in-more-than-a-decade</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 13:08:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
